quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  14,28,Alam Tará 'Ilá Al-Ladhīna Baddalū Ni`mata Allāhi Kufrāan Wa 'Aĥallū Qawmahum Dāra Al-Bawāri
  14,29,Jahannama Yaşlawnahā Wa Bi'sa Al-Qarāru
  14,30,Wa Ja`alū Lillāhi 'Andādāan Liyuđillū `An Sabīlihi Qul Tamatta`ū Fa'inna Maşīrakum 'Ilá An-Nāri
  14,31,Qul Li`ibādiya Al-Ladhīna 'Āmanū Yuqīmū Aş-Şalāata Wa Yunfiqū Mimmā Razaqnāhum Sirrāan Wa `Alāniyatan Min Qabli 'An Ya'tiya Yawmun Lā Bay`un Fīhi Wa Lā Khilālun
  14,32,Allāhu Al-Ladhī Khalaqa As-Samāwāti Wa Al-'Arđa Wa 'Anzala Mina As-Samā'i Mā'an Fa'akhraja Bihi Mina Ath-Thamarāti Rizqāan Lakum Wa Sakhkhara Lakumu Al-Fulka Litajriya Fī Al-Baĥri Bi'amrihi Wa Sakhkhara Lakumu Al-'Anhāra
  14,33,Wa Sakhkhara Lakumu Ash-Shamsa Wa Al-Qamara Dā'ibayni Wa Sakhkhara Lakumu Al-Layla Wa An-Nahār
  14,34,Wa 'Ātākum Min Kulli Mā Sa'altumūhu Wa 'In Ta`uddū Ni`mata Allāhi Lā Tuĥşūhā 'Inna Al-'Insāna Lažalūmun Kaffārun